  "description": "OURO-IV made playable. Topology 2 (Chua) at chaosIndex 0.7, leash 0.65 — the organic membrane that can hold indefinitely, the double-scroll attractor breathing at its own frequency. Mod wheel sweeps chaos from 0.7 to 0.9: the membrane thins, oscillates harder, begins approaching the boundary where the double-scroll collapses into pure stochastic motion. Aftertouch reduces damping from 0.5 toward 0.2 — press into a note and the system destabilizes slightly more with each pound of pressure. The membrane that can hold. The question is whether you will let it.",
